description.en:
The Wall Street Inu (AKA The Inu Of Wall Street) is an ETH project based on a famous Hollywood movie.

The Wall Street Inu is for all of us, crypto traders trying to make it. Here you have the long-awaited opportunity you have been looking for. Stop looking for gems because you have just found the whole treasure.

One of our plans for $WALLSTREETINU is to create a gallery for exclusive NFT’s with fantastic characters. Our designers are already working on it.

Another great idea is to create a 2D game where the user can use his tokens in exchange for items or benefits.
